<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-853] Caching does not work when using RMI</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-853</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Filters and caching uses transient maps so that caching does not work if you are using RMI and a remote searcher &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I want to add a new RemoteCachededFilter that will make sure that the caching is done on the remote searcher side &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;All &lt;/p&gt;</environment>
